  "title": "Accounts Executive",
  "description": "<h4>Job Description</h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>Handling full set of accounts which includes AR, AP, Inventory and GL</li>\n  <li>Assisting in monthly and yearly closing activities including reports and reconciliation</li>\n  <li>Preparing monthly and quarterly financial reports and accounts schedules</li>\n  <li>Preparing payment vouchers, journal entries and input into the system</li>\n  <li>Responsible for GST Submission</li>\n  <li>Liase with Auditors to coordinate the financial year end audit</li>\n  <li>Liase with Tax Consultant for providing accounts details for Income Tax Returns</li>\n  <li>Preparing of Survey and Statistics forms</li>\n  <li>Any administrative duties or ad-hoc duties assigned from time to time</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>JOB REQUIREMENTS</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Candidate must possess Degree in Accountancy or relevant qualification</li>\n  <li>Minimum 3 Year(s) full set of accounting experiences</li>\n  <li>Knowledge and hands - on experience in handling accounting software will be a plus</li>\n  <li>Good Knowledge of Microsoft Office applications</li>\n  <li>Possess initiative, good working attitude and have strong sense of responsibility</li>\n  <li>Team Player with ability to work independently</li>\n</ul>",
